T1  - The cost of market versus regulatory discipline in banking1We thank Allen Berger, David Brown, Richard Cantor, Benjamin Esty (the referee), Mark Flannery, Chris James, George Kaufman, John O'Keefe, Richard Rosen, Raj Varma, Subu Venkataraman, seminar participants at Loyola University Chicago, the Federal Reserve Board of Governors and the Australasian Finance and Banking Conference for helpful comments. Garfinkel thanks Loyola University Chicago's School of Business for financial support. Ken Kotz provided excellent research assistance. All remaining errors are our own.1
